<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Karl Ove Knausgaard, trans. by Martin Aitken, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9780593832806" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The School of Night</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Penguin Press)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;A remarkable addition to an exciting and disturbing series.&#8221;<br />
<em>–Publishers Weekly</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264352" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2026/81jz8ifat5l-_sl1500_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_.jpg" data-orig-size="1000,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Daniyal Mueenuddin, This Is Where the Serpent Lives" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-200x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-683x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264352" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-200x300.jpg" alt="Daniyal Mueenuddin, This Is Where the Serpent Lives" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-200x300.jpg 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/81jz8ifAt5L._SL1500_.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Daniyal Mueenuddin, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9780525655152" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>This is Where the Serpent Lives</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Knopf)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Brutal, funny and brilliantly told &#8230; Set to be a standout novel of 2026.&#8221;<br />
<em>–The Guardian</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="265144" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/karl-ove-knausgaard-niall-williams-daniyal-mueenuddin-and-more-21-new-books-out-today/attachment/9781639738878/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878.jpg" data-orig-size="540,810" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="John, Niall Williams" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878-200x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-265144" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878-200x300.jpg" alt="John, Niall Williams" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878-200x300.jpg 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9781639738878.jpg 540w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Niall Williams, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781639738878" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>John</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Bloomsbury)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Powerful and moving &#8230; An absorbing and intelligent novel.&#8221;<br />
<em>–Times Literary Supplement</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264356" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2026/kathleen-boland-scavengers/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers.jpg" data-orig-size="994,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Kathleen Boland, Scavengers" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-199x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-679x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264356" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-199x300.jpg" alt="Kathleen Boland, Scavengers" width="199" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-199x300.jpg 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-679x1024.jpg 679w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-768x1159.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Kathleen-Boland-Scavengers.jpg 994w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 199px) 100vw, 199px" /></p>
