<strong>(Viking)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Immensely moving and very funny.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>Megha Majumdar</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264346" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2026/winter-the-story-of-a-season/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season.jpg" data-orig-size="976,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Winter- The Story of a Season" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-195x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-666x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264346" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-195x300.jpg" alt="Winter- The Story of a Season" width="195" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-195x300.jpg 195w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-666x1024.jpg 666w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-768x1180.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-39x60.jpg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Winter-The-Story-of-a-Season.jpg 976w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 195px) 100vw, 195px" /></p>
